descriptionHtml:

Do you watch TV accompanied by your collection of Harry Potter, Star Wars and The Walking Dead figures? Then get the EMP app now and making shopping for fan merch from your favourite bands, series and films even quicker. Huge gaming fan? No problem – we’ve also got merchandise from Zelda, Resident Evil and Warcraft. You can also manage your customer account on the go and discover the latest news about festivals where you are.

✨ What are the app highlights?

Is your order already on its way to you? How can you send an item back if it doesn’t fit you? You can find all this and more info in the new EMP app. You can also join the Backstage Club here, and benefit from loads of exclusive offers. Still not enough for you? We also have the latest catalogue ready for you to browse through online.

✨ We love merchandise in every form

Motörhead, Iron Maiden and Guns N‘Roses? Or do you prefer Gothic, Rockabilly and Steampunk? No matter what your interests, with us you’ll find the right fan merch. We also have the best plus-size clothing and brands waiting for you too.

✨ Your wishlist

Save all your favourite clothes and figures on your wishlist, so that you can access them and order whenever you want. Get inspired by your personal feed and discover all the latest trends and fan products.

title: EMP App

creator: EMP / LARGE
descriptionHtml:
Do you live for your favourite band, own all their t-shirts and never miss seeing them at a festival? Do you watch TV accompanied by your collection of Harry Potter, Star Wars and The Walking Dead figures? Then get the EMP app now and making shopping for fan merch from your favourite bands, series and films even quicker. Huge gaming fan? No problem – we’ve also got merchandise from Zelda, Resident Evil and Warcraft. You can also manage your customer account on the go and discover the latest news about festivals where you are.

✨ What are the app highlights?

Is your order already on its way to you? How can you send an item back if it doesn’t fit you? You can find all this and more info in the new EMP app. You can also join the Backstage Club here, and benefit from loads of exclusive offers. Still not enough for you? We also have the latest catalogue ready for you to browse through online.

✨ We love merchandise in every form

Motörhead, Iron Maiden and Guns N‘Roses? Or do you prefer Gothic, Rockabilly and Steampunk? No matter what your interests, with us you’ll find the right fan merch. We also have the best plus-size clothing and brands waiting for you too.

✨ Your wishlist

Save all your favourite clothes and figures on your wishlist, so that you can access them and order whenever you want. Get inspired by your personal feed and discover all the latest trends and fan products.

✨ Get in touch with the crew and follow us at:

https://www.emp.co.uk/events/
https://www.facebook.com/empukofficial/
https://www.instagram.com/ empukofficial/
https://www.emp.co.uk/blog
https://twitter.com/empukofficial
https://www.youtube.com/user/EMPonline

✨ Never miss another event

Meet EMP on our stand or in the Backstage Club Area at festivals, and get exclusive merch, cold drinks and meet cool people. With the EMP Festival Map, you’ll never miss another event! Receive all the facts and news about your favourite festival and be prepared for the best season of the year.

✨ Simple payment methods

Shop in our app and choose from the following payment methods:
• VISA / MasterCard
• PayPal

✨ The new EMP app: Rock & metal to take away!

Become part of our EMP family and discover merchandise from your favourite bands and the best from the worlds of entertainment, fashion and fun together with over 6 million other like-minded fans.
Are you looking for merch and clothing from your favourite band or series? Need a cool gift for family or friends? Then you’re in the right place at the EMP Online Shop. We’ve got clothing, accessories, jewellery and more for men and women who love music, entertainment, fun and fashion as much as we do.
